<article class="c-flex-article spacing ">
<header class="c-hero">
<div class="c-hero__media enlarge js-open-modal " data-modal-img-src="https://www.outsideonline.com/sites/default/files/styles/img_1400x800/public/2020/03/19/wilderness-collective-child_h.jpg?itok=tzakInFL">
<div class="article__photo-meta">
<span data-img-caption="What does it mean to be a good man? What about a healthy and balanced one? How can we wake up a bit?" class="article__caption">What does it mean to be a good man? What about a healthy and balanced one? How can we wake up a bit?</span>
<span data-img-credit="Courtesy Chris Velasco/Wilderness Collective" data-img-credit-type="Photo" class="article__credit">(<em>Photo: </em>Courtesy Chris Velasco/Wilderness Collective)</span>
</div>
